Package: OPCC
Title: Open Ontario Postal Code Correspondence
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: person("OPCC", "Maintainers", email = "maintainers@example.org", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Source-qualified, reproducible lookups from Ontario postal codes
    to Statistics Canada 2021 census geography. Release artifacts are
    checksum-verified before use and retain their evidence source.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
Depends: R (>= 4.1)
Imports: digest, jsonlite
Suggests: testthat (>= 3.0.0), dplyr, readr, sf, knitr, rmarkdown
Config/testthat/edition: 3
VignetteBuilder: knitr
